<Body>
	<Title>内蒙古一所小学发生疑似食物中毒 68人发病</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2007年9月6日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">新华网</Participant><Location lid="l1">呼和浩特</Location><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">9月6日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">信息</Denoter></Event>：(记者 李泽兵)</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Location lid="l2">内蒙古自治区巴林左旗一学校</Location><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">9月5日</Time>发生一起学生<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>截至<Event eid="e3"><Time tid="t3" type="relTime">6日</Time><Denoter did="d3" type="operation">发稿</Denoter></Event>时，<Event eid="e4">已有<Participant sid="s4">90多名学生</Participant>到<Location lid="l4">医院</Location>接受<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">检查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5">32名学生</Participant>仍<Denoter did="d5" type="operation">留</Denoter><Location lid="l5">院</Location></Event><Event eid="e6"><Denoter did="d6" type="operation">治疗观察</Denoter></Event>，但<Event eid="e7">没有1例<Denoter did="d7" type="stateChange" polarity="negative">出现</Denoter><Object oid="o7">重症</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
     
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e8">据<Denoter did="d8" type="statement">了解</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9"><Time tid="t9" type="relTime">9月5日18时52分</Time>，<Location lid="l9">巴林左旗哈达英格学校</Location>发生一起<Participant sid="s9">学生</Participant><Denoter did="d9" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，<Event eid="e10"><Time tid="t10" type="timeInterval">至21时30分</Time>，有<Participant sid="s10,s11">68名学生</Participant><Denoter did="d10" type="stateChange">发病</Denoter></Event>，症状表现为腹痛、恶心，<Event eid="e11">随即被<Denoter did="d11" type="movement">送到</Denoter><Location lid="l11">医院</Location></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e12"><Participant sid="s12">巴林左旗卫生局局长邵建国</Participant><Denoter did="d12" type="statement">介绍</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e13"><Time tid="t13" type="relTime">6日上午</Time>，又有<Participant sid="s13,s14">一些身体感到不适的学生</Participant>被<Denoter did="d13" type="movement">送往</Denoter><Location lid="l13">巴林左旗医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e14">进行<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">检查</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e15"><Time tid="t15" type="timeInterval">截至目前</Time>，累计<Participant sid="s15">有90余名学生</Participant>在<Location lid="l15">医院</Location>接受了<Denoter did="d15" type="operation">检查</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e16"><Participant sid="s16">一些病情稳定的学生</Participant>陆续<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">出院</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e17"><Denoter did="d17" type="statement">留院观察</Denoter>的学生有<Participant oid="o17">32名</Participant></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e18">由于<Participant sid="s18">学生</Participant>集中<Denoter did="d18" type="stateChange">发病</Denoter></Event>，而临床表现为胃肠症状，<Event eid="e19"><Participant sid="s19">医生</Participant>初步<Denoter did="d19" type="operation">诊断</Denoter>为疑似食物中毒</Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e20"><Participant sid="s20">巴林左旗</Participant>立即<Denoter did="d20" type="operation">启动</Denoter>了<Object oid="o20">《食品安全事故应急预案》</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e21"><Denoter did="d21" type="operation">成立</Denoter>了以分管副旗长为组长的<Object oid="o21">现场救治指挥领导小组</Object></Event>，<Event eid="e22"><Denoter did="d22" type="movement">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l22" type="destination">医院</Location></Event><Event eid="e23"><Denoter did="d23" type="operation">组织</Denoter>救治工作</Event>，<Event eid="e24"><Participant sid="s24" type="agent">巴林左旗医院</Participant>迅速组织全院力量<Denoter did="d24" type="operation">救治</Denoter><Participant oid="o24" type="recipient">中毒学生</Participant></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e25"><Participant sid="s25,s26">赤峰市、巴林左旗两级卫生防疫部门</Participant>已对<Object oid="o25,o26">学校食堂各类食品</Object>进行了<Denoter did="d25" type="operation">采样</Denoter></Event>、<Event eid="e26"><Denoter did="d26" type="operation">封存</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e27"><Denoter did="d27 " type="operation">调查</Denoter>了解<Object oid="o27">食品的进货渠道</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e28">目前<Object sid="s28">检验结果</Object>还没有<Denoter did="d28" type="stateChange" polarity="negative">出来</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e29"><Object oid="o29">事故原因</Object>正在<Denoter did="d29" type="operation">调查</Denoter>中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>巴林左旗哈达英格学校是一所寄宿制小学，共有学生700多人。</Sentence></Paragraph>
